commands.responses
Class Response

java.lang.Object
  commands.responses.Response
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChangeTurnResponse, CreateSpeciesResponse, CreateUserResponse, DinosaursListResponse, DinosaurStatusResponse, EnterGameResponse, GrowDinosaurResponse, HighscoreResponse, LayEggResponse, LeaveGameResponse, LocalViewResponse, LoginResponse, LogoutResponse, MainMapResponse, MoveDinosaurResponse, PlayersListResponse, TurnResponse
public abstract class Response
extends java.lang.Object

Overview

The Response class is an object that represents the server response to a client requests. Responsibilities

It stores information about the server response: its stored information depends strictly by the type of response generated. See subclasses for futher information.

Collaborators

A Response object can be generated by a ResponseFactory that can build a response from a string representing the server response.
